<h3>2.4 PESTLE Deep Dive: The Macro-Environmental Factors</h3>
<h4>2.4.1 Political and Legal Implications (Data Sovereignty)</h4>
<p>In a post-GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation) world, storing user records requires extreme caution. SmartStay strictly ensures that:</p>
<ul>
<li>User passwords are mathematically irretrievable via one-way Bcrypt hashing algorithms.</li>
<li>Payment details (Credit Card PANs, CVCs) never interact with the Mongoose Database. Stripe Elements tokenizes the user&#39;s card directly from the browser to Stripe&#39;s physical PCI-DSS Level 1 servers, returning only a safe <code>clientSecret</code> and <code>paymentIntentId</code>.</li>
</ul>
<h4>2.4.2 Technological Implications (The AI Revolution)</h4>
<p>2023 and 2024 saw an unparalleled surge in the viability of Large Language Models (LLMs). Deploying human staff for 24-hour phone support is economically unviable for small luxury properties. However, previous generation Chatbots (relying on keyword matching like DialogFlow) resulted in frustrating user experiences (&quot;I didn&#39;t understand that&quot;). 
SmartStay utilizes Llama-3 (a 70-Billion parameter transformer model) accessed via Groq&#39;s high-speed inference engine. Because the model inherently understands natural language, we only need to &quot;System Prompt&quot; it with the hotel&#39;s capabilities, allowing the bot to engage in profound, contextual conversations.</p>
